I write blogs about there.

00:21:54.310 --> 00:21:56.730
I have peacekeeper
programs in 25 cities

00:21:56.730 --> 00:22:00.120
that I work with people on,
and I have especially the three

00:22:00.120 --> 00:22:00.770
in Queens.

00:22:00.770 --> 00:22:04.630
You know, because kids are
so violent, communities--

00:22:04.630 --> 00:22:05.780
we don't talk about it.

00:22:05.780 --> 00:22:09.090
One hot weekend, 60 kids
