00:22:17.120 --> 00:22:20.990
You don't talk about
it, no one gives a shit.

00:22:20.990 --> 00:22:23.970
So I want to go there--
and they do care,

00:22:23.970 --> 00:22:27.540
CNN did a series of specials,
there's some discussion--

00:22:27.540 --> 00:22:29.840
but there's no solution.

00:22:29.840 --> 00:22:32.600
But Quiet Time is a
part of a solution,

00:22:32.600 --> 00:22:35.860
or it might be even
a greater solution

00:22:35.860 --> 00:22:37.530
than people could imagine.

00:22:37.530 --> 00:22:40.320
It certainly is in other
cities where we've had success.

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:41.865
CHRIS MORROW: And the David
Lynch Foundation is doing it.

00:22:41.865 --> 00:22:42.340
RUSSELL SIMMONS:
I'm going to do it

00:22:42.340 --> 00:22:43.924
with the David Lynch
Foundation, yeah.

00:22:43.924 --> 00:22:46.006
CHRIS MORROW: They are
doing a lot in that regard.

00:22:46.006 --> 00:22:48.170
RUSSELL SIMMONS: Lots of
cities, lots of schools.

00:22:48.170 --> 00:22:50.384
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:22:50.384 --> 00:22:51.800
RUSSELL SIMMONS:
I'm on the board.

00:22:51.800 --> 00:22:54.550
We really do do
a lot in schools.

00:22:54.550 --> 00:22:56.290
AUDIENCE: Thank
you for being here.

