00:23:06.420 --> 00:23:09.960
your business decisions, how
you treat people, and in general

00:23:09.960 --> 00:23:13.020
what impact it had on
you and your businesses?

00:23:13.020 --> 00:23:18.290
RUSSELL SIMMONS: I
like to think that I'm

00:23:18.290 --> 00:23:20.120
a more compassionate person.

00:23:20.120 --> 00:23:24.050
I think I may be easier to
work for, but maybe not.

00:23:24.050 --> 00:23:26.862
You know, because I want people
to be good at what they do,

00:23:26.862 --> 00:23:28.320
and I think the
way that I motivate

00:23:28.320 --> 00:23:32.960
them is different from yelling.

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:33.627
I used to yell.

00:23:33.627 --> 00:23:34.960
What the fuck is wrong with you?

00:23:34.960 --> 00:23:35.570
Why did you?

00:23:35.570 --> 00:23:36.195
You know.

00:23:36.195 --> 00:23:37.560
I don't ever do that any more.

00:23:37.560 --> 00:23:39.050
I really don't have
any experiences

00:23:39.050 --> 00:23:41.980
lately that I can think
of that I was yelling,

00:23:41.980 --> 00:23:43.330
well fuck you, then bam.

00:23:43.330 --> 00:23:46.800
I used to do it all the time.

00:23:46.800 --> 00:23:50.700
So I think that my
relationship with my executives

00:23:50.700 --> 00:23:54.050
is different, and with
my business associates is

00:23:54.050 --> 00:23:58.540
different, and I think
I'm a lot more productive.

00:23:58.540 --> 00:24:01.850
I'm running a lot of stuff
now, three digital companies,

00:24:01.850 --> 00:24:06.410
a fashion company, a financial
service company, a music

00:24:06.410 --> 00:24:12.990
company-- there's
more-- four charities,

00:24:12.990 --> 00:24:14.890
so I'm running a
lot of stuff now.

00:24:14.890 --> 00:24:20.010
And I feel like I can do more.

00:24:20.010 --> 00:24:23.460
And also, I sleep at night.

00:24:23.460 --> 00:24:24.525
Sleep.

00:24:24.525 --> 00:24:29.780
I was an insomniac,
now I sleep well.

00:24:29.780 --> 00:24:30.280
I do better.

00:24:30.280 --> 00:24:32.363
My personal relationships,
I think, have improved.

00:24:35.660 --> 00:24:37.730
I think I'm much better.

00:24:37.730 --> 00:24:38.760
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:24:38.760 --> 00:24:40.010
RUSSELL SIMMONS: Thank you.

00:24:40.010 --> 00:24:42.730
AUDIENCE: So I
was just wondering

00:24:42.730 --> 00:24:44.750
if you've encountered
this, especially

00:24:44.750 --> 00:24:47.720
