more likely to be activists.

00:45:25.680 --> 00:45:30.190
To go outside the box, to
do what's in their heart.

00:45:30.190 --> 00:45:32.690
If they're basketball
players, they're more clear.

00:45:32.690 --> 00:45:36.040
