00:45:36.040 --> 00:45:37.920
in the moment,
they do a good job.

00:45:37.920 --> 00:45:43.310
The work is a challenge
that we accept.

00:45:43.310 --> 00:45:48.295
The relationship is a challenge,
we accept it in the present,

00:45:48.295 --> 00:45:50.706
we do our best.

00:45:50.706 --> 00:45:51.830
You gotta get the fuck out.

00:45:54.890 --> 00:45:55.960
You can be strong.

00:45:55.960 --> 00:45:58.200
You can say, no, it's
not going to work.

00:45:58.200 --> 00:46:00.200
