to find the strength.

00:46:02.895 --> 00:46:06.560
It doesn't make you complacent,
that's a misconception.

00:46:06.560 --> 00:46:08.430
And I can say that
in all certainty,

00:46:08.430 --> 00:46:15.500
you'll feel more in charge,
more confident, more awake.

00:46:15.500 --> 00:46:18.670
And so it's not about
being complacent at all.

00:46:18.670 --> 00:46:20.380
In fact, it's the opposite.

00:46:20.380 --> 00:46:21.660
And that's just my argument.

